  - type: 2
    Guid: 29909da4-86ce-4960-898d-2308afb0e612
    speaker: Fox
    DialogueText: "\u201CIf you want more information, you should <color=\"orange\">
      go to the bar</color>. But the bartender won\u2019t give you that information
      for free.. You got any coin on you?\u201D  "
    cost: {fileID: 0}
    trade: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8d822821a65625847bb4f867a5a496e6, type: 2}
    flag: 
    Position: {x: -13.6, y: -164}
  - type: 0
    Guid: 614aff0a-ad10-474d-8602-d33ffaae2f99
    speaker: Fox
    DialogueText: '"If you find anything in the bar, be sure to show it to me so
      I can explain what those objects are." '
    cost: {fileID: 0}
    trade: {fileID: 0}
    flag: 
    Position: {x: 417.6, y: 257.6}
  - type: 2
    Guid: 99d7adb8-4192-4b9b-8267-d8f0aec95c70
    speaker: Fox
    DialogueText: "\"\u201CNo? I usually <color=\"orange\">check the telephone booth</color>
      for spare change. If your luck is any good, you\u2019ll find something in there.\u201D "
    cost: {fileID: 0}
    trade: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c0ed06e2ffa20694e89703e6be73dcb0, type: 2}
    flag: 
    Position: {x: 17.6, y: 44.799995}
  - type: 2
    Guid: 13eb1a8e-13ae-434c-84f8-82c11c5bb7c9
    speaker: Fox
    DialogueText: "\u201COh, another little fish? What are you doing here? Looking
      for a big, amazing Dragon Gate? So many have come before you~ Let\u2019s see
      if you can figure it out.. Or end up like the other fishies who\u2019ve come
      before you\u2026 <color=\"orange\"> The gate is either red, green, or gold</color>,
      I can tell you that much.\u201D "
    cost: {fileID: 0}
    trade: {fileID: 11400000, guid: b9c264cce1d8264418a39a7c53088682, type: 2}
    flag: 
    Position: {x: -111.2, y: -458.4}
